name: ShockCorridor
description:
Irregular movement through a never-ending, colorized corridor. Dithering with the Stucki algorithm provides texture and continuity across the saturated palette. There are well-defined edges although they are bristling with noise. Successive rendering steps allowed for the development of a phosphor glow, increased saturation, vibrance, and contrast while purposefully keeping the frame rate and overall resolution low (constraints that serve to put us in the dreamy zone).

MPEG-4 Video
640x360x10s @ 14fps
